-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/b20570c5-76b2-4456-bce8-841075337531?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/b20570c5-76b2-4456-bce8-841075337531?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/b20570c5-76b2-4456-bce8-841075337531" class="r-y8rffk" loading="eager"/></picture></div><div data-rid="d4d2b414-ebaf-46dd-8fb1-01f10f9fa0c3" class="r-pu9ut7"><div data-rid="0f58fea5-cfac-4a50-ad92-e52ea32b143e" class="r-o3xmyr alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Why We Turned To A Compound Studied For Over 100 Years And Built <a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><u>Just Blue™</u></a> Around It</p></span></div><div data-rid="72f2c809-061e-4d91-922d-0a58d6181c87" class="r-1j3a3sl"><div data-rid="f93502b1-2656-4914-8d35-515888b262d7" class="r-s4t1fo alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>For more than a century, physicians and researchers have studied a compound called<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"> </span><a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><strong><u>methylene blue</u></strong></span></a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">.</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="347e066a-cee5-438e-a88a-ee39f99baf02" class="r-wglmb0 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Its effects on human biology, particularly cellular energy systems, are well understood.</p></span></div><div data-rid="c4f52983-1242-444c-ad1a-6153e3932a08" class="r-1y3dqy6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What’s newer is the understanding of where it matters most.</p></span></div><div data-rid="a184f709-7ca6-46d3-a5c3-cdbd800f4547" class="r-wgunpt alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>At low doses, <a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><strong><u>methylene blue</u></strong></span></a> supports a key step in cellular energy production—the point where efficiency often begins to decline. This bottleneck becomes more noticeable with stress, aging, and sustained cognitive demand.</p></span></div><div data-rid="0a3149d8-7e31-4b08-ad61-05fb1016fd28" class="r-csrrf0 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Inside mitochondria, <a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><u>methylene blue</u></a> helps electrons move more efficiently through the system, improving how much usable energy brain cells can produce.</p></span></div><div data-rid="07c53d9b-eadf-467b-a054-6123598c30a4" class="r-ud99z2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>It also helps limit inflammatory signals that interfere with efficient energy production.</p></span></div><div data-rid="3864bfb7-50fa-43f7-bba7-d283b237d820" class="r-1wohn0e alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Not as a stimulant. <br>Not as a focus drug. <br>But as a way to support the system that produces energy in the first place.</p></span></div><div data-rid="15fa27a3-878e-4ea0-a290-0e2cabc13721" class="r-hungh6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>When that system works more efficiently, the brain doesn’t feel “boosted.”</p></span></div><div data-rid="924dd751-9623-46bb-8f43-5d837133965c" class="r-9iq2cl alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Thinking feels easier. <br>Focus holds longer. <br>Mental effort drops.</p></span></div><div data-rid="6af6adf8-e2d5-431d-b9c4-2492a4f6b70e" class="r-1o6hpjk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The real insight wasn’t about forcing stimulation, it was recognizing that supporting mitochondrial energy production could support brain function <span style="color: #000000FF"><strong>WITHOUT</strong></span> stimulation.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="1fcbdebd-9d04-4663-b159-4dd35f8925dc" class="r-zs90ck"><div data-rid="13a39d19-1f59-4f20-b9fd-e7f71d44fb66" class="r-1qusb8x"><picture data-rid="452f3573-d9c8-4299-ba9d-a2f2d7cc56f6" class="r-c7tiyy"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/2384da7c-ca93-4748-a344-118167b548b0?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/2384da7c-ca93-4748-a344-118167b548b0?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/2384da7c-ca93-4748-a344-118167b548b0?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/2384da7c-ca93-4748-a344-118167b548b0" class="r-1nwbwiz" loading="eager"/></picture></div><div data-rid="666a1f3d-e3bf-4474-915e-e50803d68e55" class="r-v2o95s"><div data-rid="6b3e12cf-7cb8-4fc0-9b99-347e647a53f3" class="r-151mofa alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Does It Really Work—Or Is It Another Thing You Can’t Actually Feel?</p></span></div><div data-rid="cf34a6e4-e506-4a1a-abac-8836a3fb01c1" class="r-x041lx"><div data-rid="f0958fdc-3d5c-4fd7-817f-7a562a172793" class="r-x5cha1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Most people <em>do</em> notice a difference. <br>But it’s not the kind of product that hits all at once.</p></span></div><div data-rid="cd9b37eb-d0bb-4580-98f1-9ce64e77dc9f" class="r-1db5xvg alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>There’s no rush. <br>No jittery “boost.” <br>No crash.</p></span></div><div data-rid="d644befb-a835-4ac9-a802-03dd634e4f18" class="r-847a9x alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What people tend to notice instead is clarity returning.</p></span></div><div data-rid="ba31615b-4059-4637-b687-b88894d8427e" class="r-140sod alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Thoughts feel easier to access. <br>Focus feels steadier. <br>Mental effort drops.</p></span></div><div data-rid="2c7d3e69-9cc2-4485-bd5a-32a1b0621fb4" class="r-cp6mjh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Rather than feeling “amped,” many describe feeling more like themselves again.</p></span></div><div data-rid="d609da15-7209-4951-9ffb-c17767ce12a6" class="r-prgf2d alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>That experience lines up with what the research shows. In studies, <a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><strong><u>methylene blue</u></strong></span></a> has been associated with up to <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0046585"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><u>22% more energy flowing to parts of the brain that drive focus</u></span></a> and clarity, around <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://www.mdpi.com/2673-5261/6/3/16"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><u>35% more overall cellular energy</u></span></a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">, </span>and roughly <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/14724055/"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><u>30% improvement in how the brain converts oxygen into usable energy</u></span></a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><u>.</u></span></p></span></div><div data-rid="6b3080fd-f2a6-4cb6-b596-69a67883edc0" class="r-9o2ocy alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>For many, this shift is noticeable within the first 30 minutes and can last for several hours. It’s often subtle at first, but once it’s there, it’s easy to recognize.</p></span></div><div data-rid="ccb7c34a-cf86-4512-9d38-f203b35435fd" class="r-11bayed alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>That’s because nothing is being forced. <br>When brain cells can produce energy more efficiently, thinking naturally becomes clearer.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="1b75150c-bad1-4378-9a4e-69430d64d7ba" class="r-1nqm87i"><div data-rid="d46e7dbd-072a-407e-9032-174b1b4a950a" class="r-fj6yjd"><picture data-rid="e95c4c51-cd38-49f6-b990-baeada75b898" class="r-1dbtgh6"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/0bf88536-36b4-4819-89f4-8b6307a59f20?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/0bf88536-36b4-4819-89f4-8b6307a59f20?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/0bf88536-36b4-4819-89f4-8b6307a59f20?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/0bf88536-36b4-4819-89f4-8b6307a59f20" class="r-14uxtve" loading="eager"/></picture><picture data-rid="34c3d207-db8d-48c4-875c-8435418644e1" class="r-1imae9g"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/d4822f4b-9e43-477c-97a0-59c011a91225?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/d4822f4b-9e43-477c-97a0-59c011a91225?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/d4822f4b-9e43-477c-97a0-59c011a91225?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/d4822f4b-9e43-477c-97a0-59c011a91225" class="r-1dzu0vw" loading="eager"/></picture></div><div data-rid="6a047565-775e-4b6c-a293-3d4e0aa13e70" class="r-7wbqh2"><div data-rid="0b869b14-03ab-4957-8f8e-f863167ae4c1" class="r-41kfue alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Why Quality And Safety Matter More Than The Ingredient Itself</p></span></div><div data-rid="ac8fd4b8-b4fe-400f-8b02-7c122d98de98" class="r-1dvyjzh"><div data-rid="ed874ca6-d88b-4332-ab10-39c315453595" class="r-ro4gxk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>When a compound is intended to support cellular energy, <span style="color: #000000FF"><strong>how it’s made matters as much as what it is.</strong></span></p></span></div><div data-rid="477db20c-a25a-44d3-b90a-fe36ed52ae92" class="r-e2etx4 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><u>Methylene blue</u></a> only works as intended when it’s clean, accurately dosed, and consistently formulated. That isn’t a branding preference, it’s basic biology and pharmacology.</p></span></div><div data-rid="87a952b9-c0bd-483b-a17b-6153be72af30" class="r-hzux4r alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>In practice, this is where many products fall short.</p></span></div><div data-rid="35ba54b3-a1ab-490c-81e0-5a7af1df1ab0" class="r-1yefg0l alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Some are underdosed. Others are inconsistently mixed or sourced from industrial-grade materials never intended for human use. Liquid forms can be especially problematic, often degrading over time or failing to match what’s listed on the label.</p></span></div><div data-rid="5402e9c1-f357-4b2e-8c86-fb0221ae57f0" class="r-1dlkn7g alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Contamination is another issue most people never hear about. Certain <a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><strong><u>methylene blue</u></strong></span></a> sources have been found to contain measurable levels of heavy metals such as lead, cadmium, or mercury. Without independent testing, there’s no reliable way to know what you’re actually getting.</p></span></div><div data-rid="9e6e7ca4-a3a7-436a-825b-8edc2677d1cc" class="r-e3qctx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>As a physician, that’s not something I’m comfortable recommending or attaching my name to.</p></span></div><div data-rid="7f360c59-9b7a-443f-a874-d4ea0c73eeab" class="r-19k9efl alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>That’s why quality isn’t optional here. It’s foundational.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="648c20ad-196e-42f8-ab32-39435055e613" class="r-1k2943o"><div data-rid="90569f13-7c6b-44d0-8c06-e200043f2291" class="r-10aajjz"><picture data-rid="44302541-7ede-45f5-bb7c-48ace20eaaea" class="r-67lg8s"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/15416e16-8ffd-417d-bf35-9918bf7f7be1?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/15416e16-8ffd-417d-bf35-9918bf7f7be1?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/15416e16-8ffd-417d-bf35-9918bf7f7be1?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/15416e16-8ffd-417d-bf35-9918bf7f7be1" class="r-hc7sfh" loading="eager"/></picture></div><div data-rid="374c4701-58d1-4a3e-861d-16c8ac2d28ef" class="r-vubcd5"><div data-rid="9523748e-3109-44b9-998b-676bb61ba918" class="r-1a8zkmp alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><u>Just Blue™</u></a> Is Built To Meet True Medical Standards</p></span></div><div data-rid="435f7b3b-d226-4896-8cf9-baa0fc0311a5" class="r-diezk5"><div data-rid="7e72fd55-0292-4e8d-a972-b6ffe6601f13" class="r-19uvu0y alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><strong><u>Just Blue™</u></strong></span></a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><strong> </strong></span>was designed to meet the standards physicians expect, not the minimum standards the supplement market permits.</p></span></div><div data-rid="ee5a46eb-93f3-4f72-9aa7-7a6615870190" class="r-1f81dsl alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Dietary supplements are largely self-regulated. Manufacturers provide certificates of analysis for their ingredients, but in most cases, those documents are accepted at face value and never independently verified.</p></span></div><div data-rid="cc6a98eb-f329-4311-ace1-54a6975bdbc2" class="r-efadu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>We chose a different approach.</p></span></div><div data-rid="5b390388-cbf1-481e-a2d2-06e0e6151a75" class="r-u364of alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><strong><u>Just Blue™</u></strong></span></a> is formulated with pharmaceutical-grade<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"> </span><a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><strong><u>methylene blue</u></strong></span></a> and manufactured in an FDA-registered facility.</p></span></div><div data-rid="2c91c1c9-e95d-4dfe-bcb4-1321927ba40b" class="r-t6ssqu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Every batch comes with a certificate of analysis from the manufacturer, and is then <span style="color: #000000FF"><strong>independently tested again</strong></span> to confirm identity, potency, and purity before it’s ever released.</p></span></div><div data-rid="6a6f4ba0-6194-477f-870c-4dc5376b10c2" class="r-nw7emd alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>That additional verification step is uncommon in the supplement world, but it matters when you’re working with compounds that affect cellular energy. <br>As both a physician and a co-founder, this is the level of rigor I expect clinically, and the level I insist on personally.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="d67de7de-00e4-498e-a431-3c92de3b81ff" class="r-10mokrd"><div data-rid="3d9e7a7a-6352-4fcd-b740-df20d852485e" class="r-1a6917h"><picture data-rid="67b13622-30ae-47cb-87b5-4d8f8c8321dc" class="r-16tyxuc"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/3d7b7f95-8719-4b57-abdc-0bb3ad018ddf?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/3d7b7f95-8719-4b57-abdc-0bb3ad018ddf?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/3d7b7f95-8719-4b57-abdc-0bb3ad018ddf?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/15a4286a-0cc2-407c-9058-f94ed35b79a2/3d7b7f95-8719-4b57-abdc-0bb3ad018ddf" class="r-wjugtb" loading="eager"/></picture></div><div data-rid="af556072-73bf-45fc-95d3-a8f3a86bb376" class="r-4gsag2"><div data-rid="4f5a4ec1-5bac-4252-b808-81b29138547b" class="r-h51em5 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Trusted By People Who Can’t Afford Brain Fog</p></span></div><div data-rid="ec35a089-dbfb-409c-9527-ddf4f1138fd8" class="r-kdvk6j"><div data-rid="5d58c4d9-5b5d-40bd-8fa1-cc5b85147062" class="r-1qcokbb alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><strong><u>Just Blue™</u></strong></span></a> isn’t popular because it’s trendy. It’s used because it works reliably and consistently.</p></span></div><div data-rid="0eb30bf7-196d-4831-865c-1e44fb290223" class="r-181gm44 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>That’s why it’s been adopted by physicians, executives, athletes, and creators who depend on clear thinking every day. These are people who don’t chase stimulation or shortcuts. They look for approaches grounded in real biology, precise formulation, and safety that holds up over time.</p></span></div><div data-rid="2e48bb72-1766-49df-b8fe-518e972f61f0" class="r-1sf0z51 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>As a physician and co-founder, I stand behind <a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><strong><u>Just Blue™</u></strong></span></a> because I understand the compound, the mechanism, and the margin for error. It’s carefully formulated, independently verified, and built around a compound that has been studied in human biology for over a century—now applied where cellular energy matters most.</p></span></div><div data-rid="29b6c132-0033-45b0-9456-aee6c7d6e34b" class="r-1szhu0f alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>If brain fog has been holding you back, this offers a fundamentally different approach: <br>supporting <span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><strong><em>how</em> your brain makes energy, rather than forcing it to perform.</strong></span></p></span></div><div data-rid="39a237f3-8f2d-458f-ad03-1c1b28056619" class="r-19w95o6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><a rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/collections/troches-for-energy/products/justblue"><strong><u>Explore Just Blue™</u></strong></a></p></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
